ed="T" n="0711b05"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0711b05"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023550">洛陽廣福寺</placeName><persName key="A000774">金剛智</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0711b06"/><persName key="A000774">釋跋日羅菩提</persName>，華言<persName key="A000774">金剛智</persName><ptr target="#n87"/>。<placeName key="PL000000048353">南印度摩賴耶<lb
ed="T" n="0711b07"/>國</placeName>人也，華言<placeName key="PL000000048353">光明</placeName>，<ref target="#PL000000048353" type="place">其國</ref>境近<placeName key="PL000000048354">觀音宮殿補陀<lb
ed="T" n="0711b08"/>落伽山</placeName>。<ref target="#A017824" type="person">父</ref>婆羅門<ptr target="#n117"/>善五明論<ptr target="#n88"/>，為<placeName key="PL000000048351">建支</placeName><ptr target="#n89"/>王師。<lb
ed="T" n="0711b09"/><persName key="A000774">智</persName>生數歲，日誦萬言，目覽心傳，終身無忘。<lb
ed="T" n="0711b10"/><date key="j19708861971251" from-iso="0684-01-01" to-iso="0684-12-31">年十六</date>，開悟佛理，不樂習<persName key="A017571">尼<anchor xml:id="beg0711sgsz4"/>揵<anchor xml:id="end0711sgsz4"/>子</persName>諸論<ptr target="#n485"/>，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0711b11"/>削染出家，蓋宿<anchor xml:id="beg0711001"/>植<anchor xml:id="end0711001"/><ptr target="#n90"/>之力也。後隨師往<placeName key="PL000000048272">中印<lb
ed="T" n="0711b12"/>度那爛陀寺</placeName>，學修多羅<ptr target="#n91"/>、阿毘達磨<ptr target="#n92"/>等。洎<ref type="date" target="#j19723471972712">登<lb
ed="T" n="0711b13"/>戒法</ref>，遍聽十八部律<date from-iso="0688" key="j19723471983697" to-iso="0719"/>。又詣<placeName key="PL000000055425">西印度</placeName>學「小乘」<lb
ed="T" n="0711b14"/>諸論及瑜伽<ptr target="#n93"/>、三密<ptr target="#n94"/>、陀羅尼門<ptr target="#n95"/>。十餘年全通《三<lb
ed="T" n="0711b15"/>藏》。次復遊<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName>，登<placeName key="PL000000048735">楞伽山</placeName>，東行<placeName key="PL000000048205">佛誓</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000048221">裸<lb
ed="T" n="0711b16"/>人</placeName>等二十餘國。聞<placeName key="PL000000000083">脂那</placeName>佛法崇盛，泛舶而<lb
ed="T" n="0711b17"/>來，以多難故，累歲方至。<date key="j19836981984080" from-iso="0719-01-30" to-iso="0720-02-16">開元己未歲</date>，達于<lb
ed="T" n="0711b18"/><placeName key="PL000000030464">廣府</placeName>，勅迎就<placeName key="PL000000042410">慈恩寺</placeName>，尋徙<placeName key="PL000000042270">薦福寺</placeName>。所住之<lb
ed="T" n="0711b19"/>剎，必建大曼拏羅<ptr target="#n96"/>灌頂<ptr target="#n97"/>道場，度於四眾<ptr target="#n98"/>。<persName key="A001525">大智</persName><ptr target="#n99"/>、<lb
ed="T" n="0711b20"/><persName key="A000008">大慧</persName>二禪師、<persName key="A000095">不空三藏</persName>皆行弟子之禮焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0711b21"/>後隨<ref target="#A000291" type="person">駕</ref><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，<ref target="#d19836981984080" type="date">其年</ref>自正月不雨迨于五月，<lb
ed="T" n="0711b22"/>嶽瀆靈祠，禱之無應。乃詔<persName key="A000774">智</persName>結壇祈請。於<lb
ed="T" n="0711b23"/>是用不空鉤<ptr target="#n100"/>、依菩薩法，在所住處起壇，深<lb
ed="T" n="0711b24"/>四肘<ptr target="#n101"/>，躬繪<persName key="A004093">七俱胝菩薩</persName>像<ptr target="#n102"/>，立期以開光，明<lb
ed="T" n="0711b25"/>日定<anchor xml:id="beg0711002"/>隨<anchor xml:id="end0711002"/>雨焉。<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>使<persName key="A000008">一行禪師</persName>謹密候之。<lb
ed="T" n="0711b26"/>至第七日，炎氣爞爞，天無浮翳。午後，方開<lb
ed="T" n="0711b27"/>眉眼，即時西北風生，飛瓦拔樹，崩雲泄雨，<lb
ed="T" n="0711b28"/>遠近驚駭。而結壇之地，穿穴其屋，洪注道<lb
ed="T" n="0711b29"/>場。質明，<ref target="#PL000000023581" type="place">京城</ref>士庶皆云：「<persName key="A000774">智</persName>獲一龍，穿屋飛<pb ed="T" n="0711c" xml:id="T50.2061.0711c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0711c01"/>去。」求觀其處，日千萬人，斯乃壇法之神驗<lb
ed="T" n="0711c02"/>也。于時<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>留心玄牝<ptr target="#n17"/>，未重空門，所司希旨，<lb
ed="T" n="0711c03"/>奏外國蕃僧遣令歸國，行有日矣。侍者聞<lb
ed="T" n="0711c04"/><persName key="A000774">智</persName>，<persName key="A000774">智</persName>曰：「<ref target="#A000774" type="person">吾</ref>是梵僧，且非蕃胡，不干明勅，<ref target="#A000774" type="person">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0711c05"/>終不去。」數日，忽乘傳將之<placeName key="PL000000005471">雁門</placeName>，奉辭，<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>大<lb
ed="T" n="0711c06"/>驚，下手詔留住。<ref type="date" target="#j19840811991180">初</ref><ptr target="#n103"/>，<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>之<ref type="person" target="#A017830">第二十五公主</ref>甚<lb
ed="T" n="0711c07"/>鍾其愛，久疾不救，移臥於<placeName key="PL000000042098">咸宜外館</placeName>，閉目<lb
ed="T" n="0711c08"/>不語，已經旬朔。有勅令<persName key="A000774">智</persName>授之戒法，此乃<lb
ed="T" n="0711c09"/>料其必終，故有是命。<persName key="A000774">智</persName>詣<ref type="person" target="#A017830">彼</ref>，擇取宮中七<lb
ed="T" n="0711c10"/>歲二女子，以緋繒纏其面目，臥於地，使<persName key="A017836">牛<lb
ed="T" n="0711c11"/>仙童</persName>寫勅一紙，焚於他所，<persName key="A000774">智</persName>以密語呪之。<lb
ed="T" n="0711c12"/>二女冥然誦得，不遺一字。<persName key="A000774">智</persName>入三摩地，以<lb
ed="T" n="0711c13"/>不思議力令二女持勅詣<persName key="A005076">琰摩王</persName>。食頃間，<lb
ed="T" n="0711c14"/><ref target="#A005076" type="person">王</ref>令<ref target="#A017830" type="person">公主</ref>亡保母<persName key="A017831">劉<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>護送<ref target="#A017830" type="person">公主</ref>魂隨二<lb
ed="T" n="0711c15"/>女至，於是<ref target="#A017830" type="person">公主</ref>起坐，開目言語如常。<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>聞<lb
ed="T" n="0711c16"/>之，不俟仗衛，馳騎往于<placeName key="PL000000042098">外館</placeName>。<ref target="#A017830" type="person">公主</ref>奏曰：「冥<lb
ed="T" n="0711c17"/>數難移，今<ref target="#A005076" type="person">王</ref>遣迴，略覲<ref target="#A000291" type="person">聖</ref>顏而已。」可半日<lb
ed="T" n="0711c18"/>間，然後長逝。自爾<ref target="#A000291" type="person">帝</ref>方加歸仰焉。<persName key="A008785">武貴妃</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0711c19"/>寵異六宮，<anchor xml:id="beg0711sgsz5"/>薦<anchor xml:id="end0711sgsz5"/><ptr target="#n104"/>施寶玩，<persName key="A000774">智</persName>勸<ref target="#A008785" type="person">貴妃</ref>急造<persName key="A017832">金剛<lb
ed="T" n="0711c20"/>壽命菩薩</persName>像，又勸<persName key="A017813">河東郡王</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000023577">毘盧遮那塔</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0711c21"/>中繪像；謂門人曰：「<ref target="#A008785 #A017813" type="person">此二人</ref>者壽非久矣。」<lb
ed="T" n="0711c22"/>經數月<date key="j19902821990636" from-iso="0737-02-08" to-iso="0738-01-28"/><ptr target="#n105"/>，皆如其言，凡先覺多此類也。<persName key="A000774">智</persName>理<lb
ed="T" n="0711c23"/>無不通，事無不驗，經、論、戒律、祕呪餘書，隨<lb
ed="T" n="0711c24"/>問剖陳，如鐘<anchor xml:id="beg0711003"/>虡<anchor xml:id="end0711003"/>受<ptr target="#n106"/>。有登其門者，<persName key="A000774">智</persName>一覿<lb
ed="T" n="0711c25"/>其面，永不忘焉。至於語默興居，凝然不改，<lb
ed="T" n="0711c26"/>喜怒逆順，無有異容，瞻禮者莫知津涯，自<lb
ed="T" n="0711c27"/>然率服矣。自<date key="j19836981984080" from-iso="0719-01-30" to-iso="0720-02-16">開元七年</date>，始屆<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>，漸來<ref target="#CN0410302Z03AA #CN0610102Z07AA" type="placeName">神<lb
ed="T" n="0711c28"/>甸</ref>，廣敷《密藏》，建曼拏羅，依法製成，皆感靈<lb
ed="T" n="0711c29"/>瑞。沙門<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>欽尚斯教，數就諮詢，<persName key="A000774">智</persName>一一指<pb ed="T" n="0712a" xml:id="T50.2061.0712a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0712a01"/>授，曾無遺隱。<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>自立壇灌頂<ptr target="#n97"/>，遵受斯法，<lb
ed="T" n="0712a02"/>既知利物，請譯流通。<date key="j19851741985528" from-iso="0723-02-14" to-iso="0724-02-03">十一年</date>，奉勅於<placeName key="PL000000042260">資聖<lb
ed="T" n="0712a03"/>寺</placeName>飜出《瑜伽念誦法》<ptr target="#n107"/>二卷、《七俱胝陀羅尼》<ptr target="#n108"/>二<lb
ed="T" n="0712a04"/>卷，<placeName key="PL000000048210">東印度</placeName>婆羅門<ptr target="#n117"/>大首領直中書<persName key="A002107">伊舍羅</persName>譯<lb
ed="T" n="0712a05"/>語<ptr target="#n109"/>，<placeName key="PL000000023611">嵩岳</placeName>沙門<persName key="A008786">溫古</persName>筆受<ptr target="#n53"/>。<date key="j19877131988096" from-iso="0730-01-27" to-iso="0731-02-14">十八年</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000042270">大薦福寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0712a06"/><anchor xml:id="beg0712001"/>又<anchor xml:id="end0712001"/>出《曼殊室利五字心陀羅尼》<ptr target="#n110"/>、《觀自在瑜伽<lb
ed="T" n="0712a07"/>法》<ptr target="#n111"/>要各一卷，沙門<persName key="A000095">智藏</persName>譯語，<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>筆受<ptr target="#n53"/>，刪綴<lb
ed="T" n="0712a08"/>成文。復觀舊《隨求》<ptr target="#n112"/>本中有闕章句<ptr target="#n113"/>，加之滿<lb
ed="T" n="0712a09"/>足。<persName key="A000774">智</persName>所譯總持、印契，凡至皆驗，祕密流行，為<lb
ed="T" n="0712a10"/>其最也。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189 #PL000000023581">兩京</ref>稟學，濟度殊多，在家出家，傳之<lb
ed="T" n="0712a11"/>相繼。<date key="j19886731988673" when-iso="0732-09-13">二十年壬申八月既望</date><ptr target="#n114"/>，於<placeName key="PL000000023550">洛陽廣福寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0712a12"/>命門人曰：「白月圓時，<ref target="#A000774" type="person">吾</ref>當去矣。」遂禮<persName key="A004206">毘盧<lb
ed="T" n="0712a13"/>遮那佛</persName>，旋繞七匝，退歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023551">本院</ref>，焚香發願，頂<lb
ed="T" n="0712a14"/>戴梵夾并新譯教法，付囑訖，寂然而化。壽七<lb
ed="T" n="0712a15"/>十一，臘五十一。<date key="j19887531988753" when-iso="0732-12-02">其年十一月七日</date><ptr target="#n115"/>葬於<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍門</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0712a16"/>南<placeName key="PL000000023513">伊川</placeName>之右，建<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023830">塔</ref>旌表。傳教弟子<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>奏舉，<lb
ed="T" n="0712a17"/>勅諡國師之號。灌頂<ptr target="#n97"/>弟子中書侍郎<persName key="A008503">杜鴻漸</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0712a18"/>素所歸奉，述碑紀德焉<ptr target="#n30"/>。</p>
        <p><lb
ed="T" n="0712a19"/>系曰：五部曼拏羅法，攝取鬼物，必附麗童<lb
ed="T" n="0712a20"/>男處女，去疾除祅也絕易。近世之人，用是<lb
ed="T" n="0712a21"/>圖身口之利，乃寡徵驗，率為時所慢。吁，正<lb
ed="T" n="0712a22"/>法醨薄，一至於此！</p>
